data.description: Seller is offering a $4,000 buyer incentive! This 4-bed home is nestled in a coveted cove in Brunswick Farms. All beds down (+bonus up), providing both privacy & accessibility. Spacious greatroom & cozy hearthroom. Main bdrm is a retreat, boasting an expansive layout with a sitting area for quiet moments of relaxation. Main bath is adorned w/dble closets, ensuring ample storage. A serene outdoor XL patio backs up to wooded area, providing a natural/private backdrop. Check out YouTube video!
